": [125.0, 882.7, 526.9, 905.5]}, {"text": "We sponsor defined benefit pension plans in the U.S. and certain foreign locations. In addition, we sponsor defined contribution plans in the U.S.", "bbox": [125.0, 918.4, 1138.4, 940.9]}, {"text": "and contribute to government-sponsored retirement plans in locations outside the U.S. We also currently provide postretirement medical and life", "bbox": [125.0, 941.3, 1137.7, 963.9]}, {"text": "insurance benefits to certain U.S. employees.", "bbox": [125.0, 964.2, 441.5, 986.8]}, {"text": "Included in accumulated other comprehensive loss at November 30, 2014 was $330.0 million ($224.0 million net of tax) related to net unrecognized", "bbox": [125.0, 1010.0, 1139.5, 1032.6]}, {"text": "actuarial losses of $327.9 million and unrecognized prior service costs of $2.1 million that have not yet been recognized in net periodic pension or", "bbox": [125.0, 1033.0, 1140.7, 1055.5]}, {"text": "postretirement benefit cost. We expect to recognize $23.4 million ($15.7 million net of tax) in net periodic pension and postretirement benefit", "bbox": [125.0, 1055.9, 1127.7, 1078.4]}, {"text": "expense during 2015 related to the amortization of actuarial losses of $23.1 million and the amortization of prior service costs of $0.3 million.", "bbox": [125.0, 1078.8, 1110.2, 1101.3]}, {"text": "Defined Benefit Pension Plans", "bbox": [125.0, 1124.3, 367.6, 1147.2]}, {"text": "The significant assumptions used to determine benefit obligations are as follows as of November 30:", "bbox": [125.0, 1147.5, 828.7, 1170.1]}, {"text": "United States", "bbox": [848.0, 1190.1, 929.0, 1208.9]}, {"text": "International", "bbox": [1025.9, 1190.1, 1101.2, 1208.9]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [839.2, 1217.2, 867.0, 1236.5]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [923.6, 1217.7, 951.4, 1236.5]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [1008.0, 1217.2, 1035.7, 1236.5]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [1098.6, 1217.7, 1126.4, 1236.5]}, {"text": "Discount rate—funded plan", "bbox": [125.0, 1246.4, 300.